No McMethods Order Dates

Keystones have affected us from allowing us to have McDonalds delivered to you. On Sunday (5/11) we thought Keystones were taking place only this week.

We have now got more updates and word from staff to tell you when we are not operating McMethods due to Keystones.

These following dates, McMethods will not operate and we will not be taking any orders:

Mon-Thu 5/12, 5/13, 5/14, 5/15

Mon-Fri 5/19, 5/20, 5/21, 5/22, 5/23

We will resume McMethods & its services starting 5/27 (excluding Friday 5/16 when we are open that day). We apologize for the inconvenience this has caused.

All purchases made through us will be fufilled at the high school or PMCTC. All food is kept warm in an insulated bookbag with extra layers inside to keep warmth. All food is paid and receipted under the name "J". All food is delivered to the high school or PMCTC for you.
